title: #280: I Hate Myself (@JoeListComedy)
itunes:title: I Hate Myself with Joe List
description: Joe List invited me over to his apartment to talk about self loathing. I've always noticed that Joe has a bit of a deal with hating himself. I guess I kind of have the same thing once in a while. But List takes it to another level sometimes. We talked about that, cigars making us sick, and confidence in general.
